reviewText: Two movies on this DVD - very poor picture and sound for both of them.  I am glad I didn't spend that much money.  I actually give NO rating on this double-feature DVD. Save your money!!
The DVD arrived in excellent condition.  I would buy from this person at anytime in the future.
